      <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
      <p>
        Mat & Mind was created to provide a distraction-free environment for yoga practice.
        In today's digital world, even something as mindful as yoga can become entangled with
        addictive algorithms, endless recommendations, and attention-grabbing features.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site offers a simple solution: a curated collection of high-quality yoga videos
        that you can access without the temptations of a typical video platform. Practice
        with intention, not distraction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Why Distraction-Free?</h2>
      <p>
        Traditional video platforms are designed to maximize watch time and engagement,
        not mindfulness. Their recommendation algorithms and autoplay features can lead
        to unhealthy usage patterns and take us away from our intended practice.
      </p>
      <p>
        By creating a dedicated space for yoga videos with minimal distractions, we aim to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Help you maintain focus during your practice</li>
        <li>Eliminate the temptation to watch "just one more video"</li>
        <li>Reduce screen time while still accessing quality instruction</li>
        <li>Create a more mindful relationship with digital content</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>
        Mat & Mind takes several approaches to create a more mindful experience:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Curated Content</strong>: Only carefully selected videos make it into our collection</li>
        <li><strong>Minimal Interface</strong>: Clean design without flashy distractions</li>
        <li><strong>No Recommendations</strong>: We don't use algorithms to suggest "what to watch next"</li>
        <li><strong>Useful Controls</strong>: Simple features like 15-second jumps that enhance practice</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Storage</strong>: Access videos without downloading large files to your device</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <p>
        This site is built using <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">11ty (Eleventy)</a>,
        a simple static site generator. The videos are embedded from YouTube but with parameters
        that disable most distracting elements. The site is hosted on <a href="https://www.netlify.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Netlify</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        The project is open source and contributions are welcome. If you'd like to suggest
        videos or improvements, please visit our <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/mat-and-mind" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub repository</a>.
      </p>
